PNaCl: Reduce duplication in scripts for running GCC torture tests

Don't duplicate the logic for each architecture.

Remove some whitespace from the help text comments to make the help
text more readable.

This is in preparation for plumbing through an argument for enabling
C++ exception handling for a subset of the tests.

